20new%20ChatGPT%20feature.%20It%20only%20got%20more%20confusing%20as%20I%20searched.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20ChatGPT%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f250231c1f80efbec5c783%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatGPT%20launched%20a%20shopping%20feature%20that%20allows%20US%20users%20to%20buy%20items%20within%20their%20chat.%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20tried%20OpenAI's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-user-stats-messages-per-day-tech-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20shopping%20feature%20for%20gift%20ideas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20a%20cool%20concept%2C%20but%20I%20found%20limitations%20in%20the%20functionality.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20it%20did%20at%20helping%20me%20find%20a%20gift%20for%20my%20mom's%20birthday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20shopping%20feature%20on%20ChatGPT%20dropped%20just%20in%20time%20for%20my%20mom's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20it%20can%20help%20me%20find%20the%20right%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-market-share-700-billion-sam-altman-chatgpt-sora-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20September%2029%20that%20it%20was%20introducing%20a%20new%20shopping%20feature%20called%20Instant%20Checkout%20that%20would%20allow%20US-based%20ChatGPT%20free%2C%20Plus%2C%20and%20Pro%20users%20to%20search%20and%20purchase%20items%20right%20in%20their%20chats.%20For%20now%2C%20it's%20available%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fetsy-witch-spell-ai-slop-economy-consumer-spending-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eitems%20from%20Etsy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Shopify%20merchants%2C%20like%20Glossier%2C%20Skims%2C%20Spanx%20and%20Vuori%2C%20coming%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ChatGPT%20maker%2C%20whose%20CEO%2C%20Fidji%20Simo%2C%20hails%20from%20Instacart%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20big%20plans%20for%20shopping.%20It%20struck%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmarts-new-chatgpt-deal-shows-agent-shopping-here-to-stay-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeal%20with%20Walmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20soon%20allow%20people%20to%20make%20purchases%20from%20the%20world's%20largest%20retailer%20directly%20within%20the%20app.%20Other%20companies%2C%20including%20delivery%20apps%20Instacart%20and%20DoorDash%20and%20retailer%20Target%2C%20are%20also%20building%20shopping%20experiences%20within%20the%20AI%20chatbot.%20Some%20people%20also%20use%20ChatGPT%20as%20a%20shopping%20assistant%2C%20comparing%20things%20like%20price%20and%20style%20across%20brands%20and%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20shopping%20experiences%20to%20come%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20out%20ChatGPT's%20Instant%20Checkout%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bd4c10d-f3a9-48a0-a531-961b083c9397%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can't%20go%20wrong%20with%20jewelry%20as%20a%20gift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20birthday%2C%20my%20mom%20wants%20a%20mixed-metal%20bracelet%20made%20with%20sterling%20silver%20and%20gold%2C%20and%20I%20set%20a%20budget%20of%20%24400.%20Etsy%20sounded%20like%20a%20good%20place%20to%20find%20unique%20handmade%20jewelry%20for%20her%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20followed%20my%20chatbot's%20instructions%20by%20simply%20asking%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bshow%20me%20handmade%20silver%20and%20gold%20bracelets%20on%20Etsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221628%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20chat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f251c7cc993f9955d063a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221221%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20gave%20the%20chatbot%20my%20preferences%20and%20budget.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20for%20more%20details%2C%20such%20as%20my%20budget%20and%20style%20preference.%20It%20then%20pulled%20up%20a%20list%20of%20seven%20options%20available%20on%20Etsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20I%20started%20to%20wonder%20if%20I%20was%20doing%20something%20wrong.%20The%20options%20had%20links%20next%20to%20them%20that%20would%20take%20me%20to%20their%20Etsy%20listings%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20button%20for%20buying%20directly%20on%20ChatGPT.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20one%20of%20the%20items%20it%20suggested%20was%20a%20%242%2C400%20bracelet%20cuff%20%E2%80%94%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20budget%20I%20gave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20it%20to%20narrow%20down%20the%20search%20to%20only%20include%20items%20with%20the%20in-chat%20%26quot%3BBuy%26quot%3B%20feature%20available%2C%20to%20which%20I%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20to%20find%20listings%20that%20support%20Instant%20Checkout%20in%20ChatGPT%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20reliably%20tell%20from%20product%20data%20whether%20each%20one%20is%20eligible%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20replied%2C%20with%20bracelet%20style%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221657%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20chat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f251dc5dbc4fd10dab0a9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221243%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20struggled%20to%20find%20eligible%20items%20for%20the%20Instant%20Checkout.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0f65252-dbc5-4e21-bd64-01673f7c91ea%5C%22%3EThe%20items%20have%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20Instant%20Checkout%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20gave%20me%20a%20list%20of%20requirements%20that%20would%20make%20an%20item%20on%20Etsy%20available%20for%20Instant%20Checkout%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOnly%20US%20users%20can%20currently%20use%20ChatGPT's%20Instant%20Checkout%20for%20Etsy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20listing%20must%20be%20from%20an%20Etsy%20seller%20who%20participates%20in%20%3Cem%3EOffsite%20Ads%3C%2Fem%3E%20(those%20are%20the%20sellers%20whose%20listings%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Binstantly%20purchased%26quot%3B%20in%20ChatGPT).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20product%20shows%20%26quot%3BVisit%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BBuy%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20not%20eligible%20for%20Instant%20Checkout.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20requirement%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20availability%20on%20ChatGPT%20was%20up%20to%20each%20Etsy%20seller%2C%20not%20the%20marketplace%20itself.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20I%20realized%20that%20it%20would%20be%20harder%20than%20I%20thought%20to%20track%20down%20an%20Instant%20Checkout-eligible%20bracelet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20partners%2C%20like%20Skims%20and%20Glossier%2C%20to%20see%20if%20they'd%20rolled%20out%20yet%20since%20the%20announcement%20was%20about%20two%20weeks%20ago.%20No%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221705%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20chat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f251ee1c1f80efbec5c7c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENot%20all%20of%20the%20merchants%20named%20in%20the%20press%20release%20are%20available%20yet.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8b841fd-2b6c-4725-a603-dabf47ffede3%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20time%20to%20change%20strategies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20widened%20my%20search%20and%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20find%20necklaces%20on%20Etsy%20instead.%20I%20got%20the%20same%20results.%20Although%20OpenAI's%20press%20release%20said%20the%20feature%20is%20already%20out%20for%20US%20users%2C%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20confirm%20that%20it%20was%20available%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20confirmed%2C%20I%20asked%20it%20to%20find%20a%20few%20examples%20of%20items%20available%20to%20purchase%20through%20ChatGPT.%20Again%2C%20no%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20reliably%20confirm%20any%20specific%20items%20right%20now%20that%20%3Cem%3Edefinitely%3C%2Fem%3E%20support%20'Buy%20in%20ChatGPT%20%2F%20Instant%20Checkout'%20from%20Etsy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chatbot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20contacted%20OpenAI%20to%20see%20if%20it%20might%20be%20user%20error%2C%20and%20didn't%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20resorted%20to%20using%20ChatGPT%20to%20find%20recommendations%20for%20necklaces%20rather%20than%20use%20a%20search%20engine.%20I%20was%20pleased%20with%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221610%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f266fe5dbc4fd10dab0d77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22894%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEtsy%20was%20among%20the%20e-commerce%20sites%20suggested%20for%20finding%20a%20bracelet.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chatbot%20gave%20me%20ideas%20for%20places%2C%20like%20Etsy%20or%20Nordstrom%2C%20to%20find%20mixed-metal%20cuff%20bracelets.%20I%20got%20more%20specific%20by%20asking%20for%20brand%20names%2C%20and%20it%20listed%20places%20like%20Cartier%2C%20Pandora%2C%20and%20more%2C%20with%20pros%20and%20cons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20told%20ChatGPT%20to%20find%20me%20items%20across%20retailers%20that%20match%20my%20criteria%20and%20are%20available%20for%20purchase.%20It%20gave%20me%20a%20list%20of%20bracelets%20from%20brands%20including%20Kendra%20Scott%20and%20Mejuri%2C%20all%20of%20which%20fit%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20%E2%80%94%20though%20I%20had%20to%20prompt%20it%20again%20to%20give%20me%20direct%20links%20to%20the%20product%20listings.%20I%20wasn't%20in%20love%20with%20any%20of%20the%20options%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20my%20search%20there%2C%20with%20my%20cart%20empty%20and%20the%20search%20for%20the%20right%20bracelet%20continuing%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-shopping-on-chatgpt-with-new-instant-checkout-feature-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760866922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f251885dbc4fd10dab0a90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-shopping-on-chatgpt-with-new-instant-checkout-feature-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20recently%20launched%20Instant%20Checkout%20for%20ChatGPT.%20I%20tested%20it%20out%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20hassle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-shopping-on-chatgpt-with-new-instant-checkout-feature-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20accuses%20US%20of%20cyberattack%3A%20Beijing%20says%20sensitive%20info%20stolen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760866769000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-124685466%2Cimgsize-45486.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-accuses-us-of-cyberattack-beijing-says-sensitive-info-stolen-what-is-national-time-center%2Farticleshow%2F124685016.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security%20accused%20the%20US%20NSA%20of%20conducting%20cyberattacks%20on%20its%20National%20Time%20Service%20Center%2C%20exploiting%20mobile%20messaging%20vulnerabilities%20to%20steal%20sensitive%20data.%20The%20ministry%20stated%20these%20attacks%2C%20using%20specialized%20tools%2C%20targeted%20critical%20timing%20s