e%20are%20hoping%20to%20eat%20their%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20investors%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20interest%20in%20such%20companies%20has%20picked%20up%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomson%20Nguyen%2C%20cofounder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Saga%2C%20said%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20these%20AI%20consultancy%20startups%20will%20ever%20take%20on%20the%20established%20players.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company%20building%20AI%20infrastructure%20for%20your%20call%20center%2C%20you'll%20still%20hire%20the%20Big%20Four%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you'll%20have%20the%20budget%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20likely%20scenario%20is%20that%20these%20startups%20will%20cater%20to%20mid-market%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20making%20under%20%24100%20million%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20that%20are%20too%20small%20to%20hire%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%20or%20Bain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPromptQL%2C%20an%20enterprise%20platform%20launched%20by%20open-source%20unicorn%20Hasura%2C%20aims%20to%20automate%20some%20of%20the%20work%20of%20a%20typical%20consultant.%20It%20helps%20clients%20build%20custom%20AI%20analysts%20by%20integrating%20their%20internal%20data%20with%20the%20foundation%20models%20they%20already%20use.%20Once%20deployed%2C%20these%20AI%20analysts%20can%20perform%20tasks%20typically%20handled%20by%20data%20scientists%20or%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20continuously%20learn%20and%20adapt%20to%20their%20environments%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPromptQL%20also%20offers%20access%20to%20its%20team%20of%20expert%20engineers%2C%20who%20help%20companies%20operate%20their%20AI%20analysts%20and%20shape%20broader%20AI%20transformation%20strategies%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20%24900%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20as%20good%20as%20a%20McKinsey%20consultant%2C%20but%20it's%20instant%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanmai%20Gopal%2C%20PromptQL's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20platform's%20%26quot%3Bkiller%20feature%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20its%20capacity%20to%20provide%20%26quot%3BAI%20accuracy%20at%20scale%20without%20requiring%20messy%20data%20to%20be%20prepped%20or%20moved%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGopal%20said%20he's%20noticed%20that%20the%20consulting%20tech%20space%20has%20grown%20substantially%20in%20just%20the%20past%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year%20is%20when%20we're%20starting%20to%20see%20more%20and%20more%20specialized%20AI%3B%20AI%20that%20can%20learn%3B%20AI%20that%20can%20absorb%20the%20context%20of%20your%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20That%20means%20there%20are%20now%20significant%20opportunities%20for%20AI%20analysts%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20emerging%2C%20because%20that%20is%20where%20the%20most%20valuable%20problems%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETomasz%20Tunguz%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Theory%20Ventures%2C%20an%20investment%20firm%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20seen%20a%20spate%20of%20consulting-focused%20AI%20startups%20emerge%20in%20the%20past%20nine%20months.%20He%20said%20he's%20met%20with%20several%20of%20them%2C%20but%20hasn't%20invested%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20noticed%20five%20patterns.%20There%20are%20AI%20startups%20that%20support%20call%20centers%20and%20automate%20customer%20service%2C%20tech%20consulting%20startups%20focused%20on%20AI%20and%20software%20implementation%2C%20startups%20developing%20accounts%20payable%20and%20receivable%20automation%20tools%2C%20management%20consulting%20startups%20building%20strategic%20and%20operational%20AI%20systems%2C%20and%2C%20finally%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20segment%20of%20startups%20in%20executive%20coaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20these%20companies%20have%20landed%20funding%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParable%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20intelligence%20platform%20that%20helps%20companies%20track%20how%20their%20employees%20spend%20their%20time%2C%20announced%20a%20%2416.6%20million%20funding%20round%20in%20September.%20Profound%2C%20an%20answer%20engine%20optimization%20platform%2C%20announced%20a%20%2420%20million%20raise%20in%20August.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdialogue-ai-pitch-deck-seed-round-market-research-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDialogue%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20automates%20market%20research%2C%20announced%20a%20%246%20million%20raise%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXavier%20AI%2C%20which%20bills%20itself%20as%20the%20world's%20first%20AI%20strategy%20consultant%2C%20is%20raising%20a%20seed%20round%20expected%20to%20close%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20cofounder%20Joao%20Filipe%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20the%20whole%20AI%20environment%20is%20competitive%2C%20but%20the%20opportunity%20is%20massive%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20more%20about%20finding%20the%20kind%20of%20investors%20with%20the%20right%20fit%20and%20background%20that%20understands%20this%20problem%20(not%20just%20AI-focused%20but%20also%20with%20industry%20expertise)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20building%20in%20this%20space%20say%20their%20aim%20is%20to%20democratize%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-consulting-senior-leaders-exodus-leave-for-startups-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulting%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20not%20replace%20human%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20still%20a%20kind%20of%20consulting%20that%20a%20McKinsey%20consultant%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Gopal%20said.%20%26quot%