's%20Sindh%20province%2C%20holding%20a%20certificate%20of%20conversion%20to%20Islam%20after%20allegedly%20marrying%20a%20much%20older%20Muslim%20man.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmissing-deaf-mute-hindu-minor-girl-surfaces-in-pakistan-married-to-older-man-9482837%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20full-time%20doctor%20using%20real%20estate%20to%20hit%20financial%20independence%20sidesteps%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20and%20scales%20her%20portfolio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20home%20for%20sale%20in%20Belmont%2C%20North%20Carolina.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f256791c1f80efbec5c849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22553%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20home%20for%20sale%20in%20Belmont%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Greenberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENicole%20Shirvani%20is%20a%20full-time%20psychiatrist%20who%20invests%20in%20real%20estate%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20used%20a%201031%20exchange%20to%20avoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%20and%20scale%20her%20portfolio.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20investment%20properties%20help%20boost%20her%20savings%2C%20support%20travel%2C%20and%20secure%20her%20daughter's%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Shirvani%20experimented%20with%20rental%20real%20estate%20in%20her%2020s%20%E2%80%94%20buying%20a%20condo%20in%20Toronto%2C%20where%20she's%20from%2C%20and%20filling%20it%20with%20a%20long-term%20tenant%20%E2%80%94%20before%20taking%20a%20step%20back%20to%20focus%20on%20medical%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20student%2C%20you're%20not%20really%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20so%20I%20kind%20of%20put%20that%20to%20the%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20psychiatrist%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20finished%20training%2C%20my%20job%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20save%20some%20money%2C%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20'How%20can%20I%20invest%20in%20something%20that%20would%20appreciate%20and%20grow%2C%20and%20also%20allow%20me%20to%20save%20more%20for%20the%20future%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20estate%20checked%20both%20boxes%2C%20providing%20both%20monthly%20cash%20flow%20and%20price%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShirvani%20started%20looking%20for%20investment%20properties%20in%20southern%20Oregon%2C%20where%20she%20moved%20after%20getting%20her%20degree.%20In%202018%2C%20she%20closed%20on%20a%20duplex%20close%20to%20the%20hospital%20where%20she%20was%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20units%20was%20already%20rented%20to%20a%20traveling%20nurse%2C%20while%20the%20other%20had%20just%20been%20vacated.%20She%20spent%20about%20six%20weeks%20upgrading%20the%20vacant%20unit%20before%20finding%20a%20new%20tenant.%20Once%20both%20units%20were%20filled%2C%20she%20said%20the%20cash-on-cash%20return%20was%20between%2015%25%20and%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22971edf19-6da8-4a86-8f8b-84615abf9789%5C%22%3EUsing%20a%201031%20exchange%20to%20sidestep%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20and%20scale%20her%20portfolio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Shirvani%20accepted%20a%20job%20in%20Florida%20and%20decided%20to%20sell%20the%20Oregon%20duplex.%20Typically%2C%20when%20you%20sell%20an%20investment%20property%20for%20more%20than%20you%20paid%20for%20it%2C%20you'll%20owe%20tax%20on%20the%20difference%3A%20either%20short-term%20capital-gains%20tax%20(if%20you%20held%20the%20property%20for%20a%20year%20or%20less)%20or%20long-term%20capital-gains%20tax%20(if%20you%20held%20the%20property%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%201031%20exchange%2C%20also%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blike-kind%20exchange%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20strategy%20that%20allows%20investors%20to%20defer%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20on%20the%20sale%20by%20reinvesting%20the%20proceeds%20into%20a%20new%2C%20similar%20property%20that%20is%20of%20equal%20or%20greater%20value%20than%20the%20relinquished%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20rules%20to%20consider%3A%201031%20exchanges%20are%20intended%20for%20investment%20properties%2C%20not%20primary%20homes%3B%20you%20need%20to%20hire%20a%20qualified%20intermediary%20to%20handle%20the%20transaction%3B%20and%20you%20have%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20time%20to%20complete%20the%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20you%20sell%2C%20the%20clock%20starts%3A%20You%20must%20identify%20your%20replacement%20property%20or%20properties%20(you%20can%20identify%20as%20many%20as%20three%20like-kind%20properties)%20in%20writing%20within%2045%20days%20of%20selling%20the%20first%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20you%20must%20close%20on%20the%20replacement%20property%20within%20180%20days%20of%20your%20initial%20property%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShirvani%2C%20who%20traded%20in%20her%20duplex%20for%20two%20properties%20in%20Florida%20%E2%80%94%20a%20beachside%20condo%20and%20a%20single-family%20home%20%E2%80%94%20said%20the%20timeline%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20stressful%2C%20but%20the%20market%20was%20still%20fairly%20busy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20started%20looking%20at%20exchange%20properties%20before%20listing%20the%20duplex%20to%20give%20herself%20plenty%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20you%20sell%2C%20try%20to%20have%20the%20replacement%20properties%20identified%20and%20line%20everything%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20advised.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20sell%20a%20house%2C%20not%20be%20able%20to%20find%20suitable%20properties%2C%20and%20be%20stuck%2C%20unable%20to%20invest%20that%20money%20into%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShirvani%2C%20who%20has%20since%20added%20two%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20the%20Shenandoah%20Valley%20and%20a%20triplex%20in%20Lakeland%2C%20Florida%2C%20to%20he