-quit-corporate-entrepreneur-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20her%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBothur%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20believes%20the%20future%20of%20business%20communication%20is%20in%20corporate%20influencing.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20technology%20and%20so%20many%20businesses%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20speak%20the%20same%20language.%20They%20don't%20understand%20each%20other.%20It's%20a%20huge%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20there%20are%20major%20career%20opportunities%20in%20this%20field.%20Since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-australia-issues-refund-ai-assurance-project-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaving%20Deloitte%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20go%20freelance%20this%20October%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20been%20overwhelmed%20by%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20her%20own%20career%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Binspire%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20tech%20translators%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20her%20top%20tips%20for%20building%20a%20career%20as%20a%20corporate%20influencer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246628116-acbe-444d-a31d-4eb2577cb76a%5C%22%3EAlign%20your%20values%20with%20your%20company%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20represent%20a%20company%2C%20the%20first%20step%20is%20making%20sure%20your%20values%20are%20aligned.%20You%20can't%20have%20different%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Bothur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20own%20role%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-accenture-job-fears-doge-consulting-contracts-trump-musk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDeloitte%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%20developed%20naturally.%20Leaders%20who%20knew%20about%20her%20marketing%20background%20invited%20her%20to%20help%20with%20a%20campaign%2C%20translating%20ideas%20from%20various%20tech%20departments%20into%20approachable%20narratives.%