3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20app%20or%20game%20I've%20built%20has%20been%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%20in%20my%20own%20life.%20I%20was%20a%20skinny%20kid%20growing%20up%20and%20tried%20going%20to%20the%20gym%20to%20put%20on%20weight%2C%20but%20learned%20very%20quickly%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-who-lost-weight-share-diet-before-after-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20results%20come%20from%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20cofounders%20and%20I%20set%20out%20to%20build%20a%20calorie-tracking%20app%20that%20integrates%20AI%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20San%20Francisco%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20after%20launching%20with%20one%20of%20the%20other%20cofounders%2C%20and%20we%20spent%20the%20summer%20of%20our%20junior%20year%20in%20high%20school%20there%20alone%2C%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us%2C%2017-year-olds%2C%20building%20out%20the%20team%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-cofounded-million-dollar-app-cal-ai-with-teen-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOur%20app%20really%20took%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20next%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20bringing%20us%20to%20now%2C%20where%20we%20are%20a%2030-person%20team%20and%20generating%20around%20%2430%20million%20in%20annual%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22181e3343-5265-42bf-8e49-6bcbf6c50f32%5C%22%3EI've%20been%20coding%20since%20I%20went%20to%20coding%20camp%20at%207%20years%20old%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20put%20me%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexecutives-weigh-in-on-learn-to-code-advice-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoding%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%207.%20I%20didn't%20learn%20that%20much%2C%20but%20it%20sparked%20my%20interest%20and%20showed%20me%20what%20was%20possible.%20YouTube%20taught%20me%20the%20rest.%20I%20would%20spend%20hours%20a%20day%20watching%20people%20program%20different%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Casi