orking%20on%20it%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20Cal%20AI%20became%20more%20established.%20We%20realized%20this%20wasn't%20just%20a%20flash%20in%20the%20pan%2C%20but%20something%20we%20could%20actually%20scale%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20beautiful%20and%20proudest%20moments%20in%20my%20life%20so%20far%20have%20probably%20been%20meeting%20people%20in%20person%20who%20show%20me%20Cal%20AI%20on%20their%20phone.%20It's%20awesome%20to%20see%20that%20something%20I%20built%20is%20being%20used%20by%20people%20every%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247ef2262-c059-4912-b8ec-00ce98a576e8%5C%22%3EMy%20best%20advice%20for%20starting%20an%20app%20is%20very%20simple%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20to%20anyone%20would%20be%20to%20get%20started.%20Ignore%20the%20noise%2C%20ignore%20the%20people%20telling%20you%20that%20it's%20impossible%20to%20do%20it%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20and%20ignore%20the%20people%20trying%20to%20push%20you%20down%20a%20specific%20path%20to%20accomplish%20your%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20becoming%20easier%20and%20easier%20to%20be%20a%20founder.%20There's%20a%20reason%20the%20age%20of%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-geniuses-child-prodigies-inventing-founding-science-business-tech-solutions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentrepreneurial%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20the%20headlines%20is%20getting%20younger.%20I%20had%20Google%2C%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20YouTube%20as%20my%20tools%2C%20but%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20founders%2C%20it's%20ChatGPT%20that%20they%20can%20use%20to%20teach%20themselves.%20Which%20is%20so%20much%20easier%20than%20watching%20YouTube%20videos%2C%20where%20I%20was%20limited%20to%20the%20content%20library%20that%20people%20have%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222de46c4d-8a7e-4f72-977d-5d2c867965ae%5C%22%3EI'm%20still%20finding%20the%20balance%20between%20being%20a%20college%20student%20and%20a%20founder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D