B%20music%20video%20on%20TV%2C%20mesmerized%20by%20lead%20singer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusicians-voice-acting-characters-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJames%20Hetfield's%20voice%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20music%20that%20was%20raw%20and%2C%20well%2C%20foreign.%20Standing%20in%20the%20same%20room%20as%20him%20decades%20later%20felt%20surreal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20big%20moment%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20texted%20some%20colleagues%2C%20trying%20not%20to%20sound%20like%20I%20was%20having%20an%20existential%20crisis%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20corporate%20metal%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a011f8f1-05b4-4e5d-a0ab-58939f4450ee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMetallica%2C%20McConaughey%2C%20and%20mosh%20pits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20doors%20opened%20at%206%2C%20though%20Metallica%20didn't%20take%20the%20stage%20until%20nearly%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20later.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Dreamfest%20felt%20like%20a%20trade%20show%20trying%20on%20a%20leather%20jacket.%20People%20milled%20around%20with%20free%20beers%20and%20wine%3B%20Salesforce%20mascots%20danced%20in%20the%20mosh%20pit%3B%20and%20the%20smell%20of%20pizza%20and%20fries%20filled%20the%20air.%20I%20spotted%20one%20guy%20in%20a%20%26quot%3BRide%20the%20Lightning%26quot%3B%20T-shirt%2C%20surrounded%20by%20a%20sea%20of%20business%20casual%20attire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20minutes%20before%20Metallica%20came%20onstage%2C%20McConaughey%20appeared%20wearing%20a%20long%20coat%20and%20a%20cap%20that%20looked%20like%20it%20had%20wandered%20in%20from%20another%20movie%20set.%20He%20announced%20that%20Dreamfest%20had%20raised%20%249%20million%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenioff-childrens-hospital-opens-roaming-robots-and-futuristic-scan-rooms-2015-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUCSF%20Benioff%20Children's%20Hospitals%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20told%20us%2C%20earnestly%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Brock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%2C%20a%20mix%20of%20sales%20reps%2C%20engineers%2C%20and%20consultants%20who%20probably%20hadn't%20rocked%20since%20college%2C%20roared%20on%20cue.%20Then%2C%20as%20the%20smoke%20machines%20and%20blinding%20lights%20kicked%20in%2C%20Metallica%20launched%20into%20%26quot%3BCreeping%20Death%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20world's%20most%20professionally%20networked%20rock%20concert%20got%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%2090%20minutes%2C%20the%20band%20ripped%20through%20a%20greatest-hits%20set%20that%20spanned%20four%20decades%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20Whom%20the%20Bell%20Tolls%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Unforgiven%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSad%20but%20True%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMaster%20of%20Puppets%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BEnter%20Sandman%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHetfield%2C%20equal%20parts%20metal%20god%20and%20stand-up%20comic%2C%20seemed%20amused%20by%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20many%20tech%20guys%20does%20it%20take%20to%20screw%20in%20a%20light%20bulb%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%20%26quot%3BNone.%20They%20call%20a%20tradesman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20booed%20pop%20singer%20Benson%20Boone's%20simultaneous%20show%20across%20the%20street%2C%20Hetfield%20grinned.%20%26quot%3BHey%20now%2C%20no%20booing!%20I%20wanna%20see%20those%20backflips!%26quot%3B%20(again%2C%20this%20is%20a%20Benson%20Boone%20reference.%20I%20had%20to%20Google%20this).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20surreal%20sight%3A%20thousands%20of%20Salesforce%20employees%20and%20people%20buying%2C%20using%2C%20and%20selling%20Salesforce%20software%2C%20headbanging%20under%20strobe%20lights%20and%20trading%20high-fives%20between%20songs.%20Somehow%2C%20it%20all%20made%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%20that%20I've%20never%20thought%20much%20about%20Salesforce%20beyond%20the%20letters%20%26quot%3BC%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BR%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BM%2C