ajor%20banks%20to%20see%20if%20they%20can%20get%20a%20loan%20or%20forbearance.%20So%20far%2C%20prospects%20have%20been%20grim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20pay%20covers%20me%20through%20October%20but%20if%20the%20shutdown%20continues%20past%20October%20into%20November%20I%20won't%20have%20enough%20savings%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DoD%20worker%20said.%20It's%20been%20a%20stressful%20time%2C%20they%20said%2C%20as%20they%20scramble%20to%20get%20last-minute%20credit%20card%20and%20loan%20applications%20together.%20They've%20already%20applied%20for%20a%20bridge%20loan%20from%20the%20United%20States%20Senate%20Federal%20Credit%20Union.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20wished%20that%20we%20could%20get%20more%20financial%20support%20from%20these%20public%20companies%20(even%20major%20ones)%20when%20it%20was%20not%20our%20fault.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20employee%20said%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20secure%20a%20mortgage%20loan%20approval%20this%20month%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthat%20fell%20through%20because%20of%20the%20missing%20paycheck%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration%20employee%20said%20that%20they're%20delaying%20repairs%20to%20their%20roof%20and%20car.%20One%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20worker%20said%20medical%20challenges%20would%20become%20%26quot%3Bdrastically%20more%20expensive%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20lost%20their%20job.%20Another%20IRS%20employee%20said%20they're%20anxious%20about%20making%20credit%20card%20and%20loan%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECochran%20and%20others%20added%20that%20they%20are%20worried%20about%20how%20their%20diminished%20spending%20will%20impact%20small%20businesses%20in%20their%20community.%20A%20few%20said%20they%20are%20working%20with%20colleagues%20to%20organize%20food%20drives%20or%20apply%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-affected-government-shutdown-national-parks-social-security-usps-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESNAP%20and%20unemployment%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20after%20the%20shutdown%20began%2C%20unemployment%20claims%20in%20DC%20started%20to%20spike%2C%20while%20an%20analysis%20by%20The%20Century%20Foundation%20found%20that%20around%2010%2C500%20federal%20workers%20across%20the%20country%20have%20filed%20for%20unemployment%20since%20the%20shutdown%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FhTPge%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FhTPge%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20are%20looking%20for%20stopgaps%2C%20too.%20USAA%2C%20which%20offers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usaa.com%2Fsupport%2Fgovernment-shutdown-program%2F%3Fakredirect%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest-free%20loans%20equivalent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20paychecks%20for%20impacted%20federal%20workers%2C%20said%20that%20they've%20approved%20and%20funded%20nearly%20%24243%20million%20for%20around%2065%2C000%20loans%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20opening%20the%20program.%20The%20Maryland%20Department%20of%20Labor%20received%20more%20than%20550%20applications%20between%20October%206%20and%20October%2014%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flabor.maryland.gov%2Ffederalworkers%2Fshutdownloan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20worker%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20the%20Navy%20Federal%20Credit%20Union%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navyfederal.org%2Fabout%2Fgovernment-shutdown.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffers%20a%20similar%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20they're%20%26quot%3Bseeing%20a%20significant%20uptick%20in%20participation.%26q