ld%20Business%20Insider%20that%20some%20employees%20received%20incorrect%20notifications%20and%20%26quot%3Bare%20not%20subject%20to%20the%20reduction%20in%20force.%26quot%3B%20The%20CDC%20union%20confirmed%20that%20%26quot%3Baround%20700%20employees%20received%20emails%20rescinding%20their%20illegal%20terminations.%20More%20than%20600%20workers%20remain%20unjustly%20fired.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20CDC%20workers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20job%20security%20is%20having%20a%20tangible%20impact%20on%20their%20lives%20and%20financial%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20emergency%20cushion%2C%20but%20I%20am%20concerned%20about%20how%20long%20it's%20going%20to%20go%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20laid-off%20CDC%20worker%20%E2%80%94%20who%20wasn't%20called%20back%20%E2%80%94%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20talked%20about%20selling%20our%20house%20if%20we%20need%20to.%20We've%20also%20talked%20about%20tapping%20into%20retirement%20savings%20as%20a%20very%20last%20resort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20CDC%20employee%20mistakenly%20received%20the%20layoff%20email.%20They%20said%20they're%20the%20breadwinner%20for%20their%20family%2C%20and%20have%20considered%20cutting%20back%20on%20activities%20for%20their%20kids%20and%20applying%20for%20an%20emergency%20loan.%20Over%20the%20past%20eight%20months%20of%20DOGE%20firings%20and%20the%20government%20shutdown%2C%20the%20employee%20said%20they%20have%20had%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20charged%20conversations%20about%20what%20our%20life%20is%20going%20to%20look%20like%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20relief%20if%20I%20still%20have%20a%20job%20and%20I%20know%20where%20my%20next%20paycheck%20is%20going%20to%20come%20from%20when%20the%20shutdown%20ends%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20ground%20has%20been%20shaken%20beneath%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnumber-workers-fired-doge-trump-musk-challenger-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOver%20200%2C000%20federal%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs%2C%20and%20thousands%20more%20have%20left%20their%20government%20posts%20through%20retirement%2C%20buyouts%2C%20quits%2C%20and%20deferred%20resignations%20since%20Trump%20took%20office%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20have%20not%20yet%20reached%20a%20funding%20agreement%20to%20end%20the%20government%20shutdown.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20encouraging%20the%20Democrats%20to%20stop%20the%20pain%20and%20reopen%20the%20government%20with%20the%20bipartisan%20funding%20proposal%20they%20supported%20just%206%20months%20ago%20and%2013%20times%20under%20Biden%2C%26quot%3B%20Abigail%20Jackson%2C%20a%20White%20House%20spokesperson%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20some%20employees%20are%20draining%20their%20bank%20accounts%20to%20show%20up%20for%20unpaid%20shifts%20until%20they%20can't%20afford%20it%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGas%20stations%20don't%20take%20IOUs.%20I%20talked%20to%20a%20couple%20employees%2C%20they%20said%2C%20'this%20is%20my%20last%20fill-up%20and%20I%20won't%20have%20any%20money%2C'%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20credit%20cards%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20literally%20like%2C%20this%20is%20the%20last%20tank%20of%20gas%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20until%20I%20get%20paid%20again.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20this%20is%20just%20too%20much.%20People%20are%20asking%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20I'd%20love%20to%20come%20work%20%E2%80%94%20but%20may%20not%20have%20gas%20money.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%20and%20Taylor%20Rains%20contributed%20reporting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-wallets-paycheck-to-paycheck-government-shutdow