20through%20October%2022%2C%20comes%20at%20a%20challenging%20time%20for%20the%20medical%20and%20scientific%20community%3A%20Vaccine%20hesitancy%20continues%20to%20spread%2C%20grant%20funding%20dwindles%2C%20and%20the%20government%20publicizes%20false%20claims%20about%20Tylenol's%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20how%20infectious-disease%20leaders%20in%20research%20and%20clinical%20care%20are%20working%20through%20this%20era%2C%20Business%20Insider%20will%20be%20on%20the%20ground%20for%20talks%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisease-prevention-ideas-us-could-learn-from-uk-israel-canada-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epublic%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategy%2C%20healthcare%20innovation%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20careers%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20ID%20Week%20will%20center%20on%20themes%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-could-transform-post-pandemic-healthcare-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20in%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20biopreparedness%20for%20infectious%20disease%20outbreaks%2C%20Dr.%20Yohei%20Doi%2C%20an%20ID%20Week%20chair%20representing%20the%20Infectious%20Disease%20Society%20of%20America%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20presenters%20who%20are%20experts%20in%20public%20health%2C%20and%20we're%20looking%20forward%20to%20hearing%20their%20insights.%20I%20think%20public%20health%20has%20always%20been%20a%20theme%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20heavily%20featured%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Doi%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210581b23-67f9-4c1e-8710-eb0b16d8e849%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20expect%20during%20ID%20Week%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EID%20Week%20is%20a%20convergence%20of%20six%20professional%20organizations%20with%20different%20specialties%3A%20the%20Infectious%20Diseases%20Society%20of%20America%2C%20the%20Society%20for%20Healthcare%20Epidemiology%20of%20America%2C%20the%20HIV%20Medicine%20Association%2C%20the%20Pediatric%20Infectious%20Diseases%20Society%2C%20and%20the%20Society%20of%20Infectious%20Diseases%20Pharmacists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGet%20ready%20for%20a%20bunch%20of%20nerds%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Sophie%20Katz%2C%20a%20pediatric%20infectious-disease%20doctor%20at%20Vanderbilt%20University%20Medical%20Center%20and%20an%20ID%20Week%20workshop%20presenter%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20interesting%20talks%20to%20go%20to%20at%20once%2C%20so%20it's%20hard%20to%20choose%20what%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Katz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20fun%20to%20be%20in%20an%20environment%20with%20all%20of%20these%20people%2C%20learning%20about%20all%20the%20things%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20science%20for%20ID.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20pre-event%20media%20briefing%2C%20a%20selection%20of%20researchers%20teased%20their%20upcoming%20ID%20Week%20presentations%2C%20which%20will%20highlight%20study%20findings%20on%20topics%20like%20the%20benefits%20of%20RSV%20and%20shingles%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoi%20said%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20attendees%20are%20medical%20doctors%2C%20with%20smaller%20yet%20growing%20subsets%20of%20pharmacists%2C%20nurse%20practitioners%2C%20and%20physician%20assistants%20attending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%20%E2%80%94%20which%20offers%20more%20than%20250%20events%20over%20four%20days%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efeatures%20talks%20on%20topics%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEmerging%20infectious%20diseases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAntimicrobial%20stewardship%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20in%20healthcare%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPediatric%20bacterial%20infections%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrescription%20research%20and%20clinical%20best%20practices%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESustainability%20and%20equity%20in%20infectious-disease%20treatment%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20is%20also%20a%20useful%20networking%20opportunity%2C%20especially%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-student-stanford-week-in-my-life-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedical%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Doi.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20ID%20Week%20BugCrawl%20program%20provides%20curated%20networking%20opportunities%20and%20lectures%20for%20students%20and%20residents.%20There's%20also%20the%20NextGen%20ID%20Lounge%2C%20a%20space%20inside%20the%20Georgia%20World%20Congress%20Center%20where%20medical%20students%2C%20residents%2C%20and%20fellows%20can%20mingle%20and%20listen%20to%20career-oriented%20talks%20by%20more%20seasoned%20infectious-disease%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20probably%20their%20first%20big%20meeting%20to%20attend%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20huge%20venue%2C%20so%20we%20have%20sessions%20where%20we%20walk%20through%20the%20conference%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Doi%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20get%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20most%20prominent%20people%20in%20the%20field%2C%20and%20just%20sit%20with%20and%20talk%20with%20them%20about%20life%2C%20career%2C%20and%20the%20research%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20are%20scheduled%20receptions%2C%20meet-ups%2C%20and%20group%20dinners%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20professional%20organizations%2C%20like%20IDSA%20and%20PIDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229c63eb7-a129-4e9e-9b07-a87700b4167a%5C%22%3EAn%20infectious%20disease%20conference%20in%20the%20mecca%20of%20US%20public%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20also%20located%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20makes%20the%20city%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mecca%20of%20public%20health%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Doi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20ID%20Week%20plans%20to%20feature%20insights%20from%20experts%20formerly%20affiliated%20with%20the%20CDC%20and%20current%20CDC%20workers%2C%20though%20their%20availability%20is%20subject%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20there%20are%20evolving%20circumstances%20with%20the%20government%20shutdown%2C%20so%20we%20have%20to%20plan%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Doi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20we're%20still%20hoping%20to%20leverage%20our%20location%20to%20the%20extent%20possible%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfectious-disease-experts-id-week-atlanta-ai-public-health-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760858094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e816ca5dbc4fd10daa91b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfectious-disease-experts-id-week-atlanta-ai-public-health-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%2010%2C000%20experts%20and%20students%20focused%20on%20infectious%20disease%20research%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20public-health%20strategy%20are%20attending%20ID%20Week%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnaftulin%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Naftulin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfectious-disease-experts-id-week-atlanta-ai-public-health-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meesho%20files%20updated%20IPO%20papers%2C%20aims%20to%20raise%20up%20to%20%24800%20million%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760857716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F30%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F1200X630%2F1717009818-7438.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Fmeesho-updated-ipo-filing-raise-800-million-sebi-offer-for-sale-125101900047_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22